flavor_text_entries.gold:
It rubs its snout
on the ground to
find and dig up food. It sometimes
discovers hot
springs.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
If it smells some­
thing enticing, it
dashes headlong off to find the
source of the
aroma.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It uses the tip of
its nose to dig
for food. Its nose is so tough that
even frozen ground
poses no problem.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
SWINUB roots for food by rubbing its
snout against the ground. Its favorite
food is a mushroom that grows under the cover of dead grass.
This POKéMON occasionally roots out
hot springs.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
Swinub excels at sniffing out mushrooms buried beneath grass or
snow. Since ancient times, the people of Hisui have often relied
upon this skill.
